name: Nukad Tampaksiring
address: Jl. Pertiwi Brata, Selat, Kec. Tampaksiring, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80552, Indonesia
review 1:
A riverside restaurant with great natural view. The food and beverage are very affordable and imo are quite good.

The motorcycle parking is quite challenging but there are a lot of spaces available.

No minimum order for any type of seatings.
review 2: It's out of all my expectations, the sight is wonderful till Im thinking that the owner had decided to choose great locations to open the business,, the food was delicious with great service,, would definitely come back again in another time,
review 3:
Beautiful location
Delicious food and drinks
Friendly, helpful staff
Able to pay by card which is useful
Impressed by how well they maintain the stunning area including gardening
review 4:
It's a mixed experience visiting this natural restaurant. The ambiance is so pleasant and relaxing as it's located nearby the river with lots of greenery and beautiful plants. Suitable to visit with family and friends, the seating is so comfortable with different level and type of table. Perfect to take pictures. Food tastes so good as we order grilled chicken with condiment and sauce. Very reasonable for the price without additional tax and service.

Yet, there are still things to improve! Seating is sometimes wet when it's raining so need to choose wisely for the location. Their service is so slow and quite unresponsive. Staffs don't work effectively therefore our order was served quite long time. For the beverage, we ordered Lime Tea and Lychee Squash, but it was so plain, barely any flavor or sweetness inside. The table wasn't properly clean as they didn't pick up the dirty dishes immediately from the previous visitors. Please pay attention to the cleanliness!
review 5:
A lovely place by the river, surrounded by lush greeneries and some waterfalls.

The food is good though limited in options with resonable price.

The staff are friendly and attentive, and service is quite fast.

Would be better if they don't have speakers playing pop music.

name: Aksha Riverside Ubud
address: Jl. Pertiwi Brata, Tampaksiring, Kec. Tampaksiring, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80552, Indonesia
review 1:
I have spent 1 week here, and I really recommande you this place. You location is just perfect for people who need to reconnect. The place is very quiet, calm and relax ! You can have a swim on the river, do mediation on the temple, and do tubing activity on the river.
The owner are very very kind and nice .
I really loved this place.

name: Warung ala pulaga
review 1: This is small restaurant with a peaceful scenery. It’s also a spacious garden and The surroundings is rice field and coconut trees. The owner is very friendly, kindly and enthusiastic. They give us a lot of fruits in your garden. The price is very affordable with 30-50idr/person
review 2: Exceptional homemade food! Everything was yummy and the price was more than worthy. The owner (Nyoman) brought us inside his stunning house and showed us around. 100% recommended if you want to eat excellent food and connect with the Balinese vibe. Thank you!
review 3: Really good food made by the warung’s owner. He even invited us to cook the desert with him. Such a unique experience and the best warung we’ve been near Ubud.
review 4: Amazing view. Friendly staff, really good prices, value for money, tasty local food. The only thing to improve is the speed for cooking the food.
review 5:
Great little Warung to experience local culture. I was riding my motorbike by and saw a sign for cafe/coffee and thought it the perfect place to take a rest.

Very friendly owner (English speaking if that’s helpful for you) & family, made me a papaya smoothie from his orchard. Beautiful views and no tourists to be found.

name: warung D'campuhan
address: Jl. Pertiwi Brata No.200, Selat, Kec. Susut, Kabupaten Bangli, Bali 80552, Indonesia
review 1: Wonderful hidden place at the river! Clean an comfy rooms! Very good food and friendly owner… ❤️
review 2: Nice local restaurants near river. Pit stop for river tubing. Yummy chicken and fried banana.
review 3:
This restorant is very natural location. You can swin or just enjoying the green environmet there during dining in.
The staffs are friendly and helpful.
Try grilled chicken and orange jus.
review 4:
Good food, nice people and wonderful location.

Prices are really cheap!
